To build for 64bit, open x64 native tools console for Visual Studio

For Windows:
scons platform=windows target=release -j2

For Android export template:
scons platform=android target=release -j2

then go to:

C:\godot> cd platform/android/java

type:
C:\godot\platform\android\java> gradlew build


clean up a build:
scons -c

scons --clean [targets]
scons --no-cache [targets]